verses.text:
and what he did to the army of Egypt, to their horses, and to their chariots;
how he made the water of the Red Sea to overflow them as they pursued you, and how the LORD has destroyed
them to this day;

and what he did to Dathan and Abiram, the sons of Eliab, the son of Reuben—how
the earth opened its mouth and swallowed them up, with their households, their tents, and every living
thing that followed them, in the middle of all Israel;
